 WHY LITHIUM?Lithium enjoys one of the strongest growth profiles out of any mined mineral today. With the increasing number of end uses for light, portable, reliable energy storage for our increasingly mobile world, lithium demand is expected to remain one of the top demand growth stories over the next decade and beyond. Please Click Here for Enertopia May 2017 Presentation+more

