Corporate — Enertopia Corporation














































































Corporate

























































Corporate OverviewMissionOur mission is to empower people by living a healthier and increased quality of life. Core ValuesOur core values of integrity, community, innovation, and excellence help to define our corporate practices and demonstrate our dedication in providing healthier, cleaner and a more sustainable environment.IntegrityOur core values and our strict compliance with all laws, rules, regulations and corporate policies that apply to our public company and business segments provide our investors with peace of mind.  It is this same uncompromising commitment that makes us work for you each day ensuring that the same commitment is provided by our consultants, business and service providers.CommunityWe have a corporate community that is focused on working together to accomplish research and development goals along with commercial and corporate objectives.  We value respect for one another in all our partnerships and to support one another collectively on our projects.InnovationInnovation is a necessity to move forward.  We are striving to provide new benefits and opportunities through new solutions for our investors and our community.ExcellenceOur unwavering adherence to our core values of honesty, integrity and commitment in the pursuit of only the best opportunities in our quest for excellence. 

