Enertopia Corp.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 12:30 PM ET
Personal Products

Company Overview of Enertopia Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Enertopia Corp., a development stage company, focuses on pursuing business opportunities in the natural resource sector in Canada. The company has an option to purchase a 100% interest in the lithium projects covering an area of approximately 2,560 acres of placer mining claims in Churchill, Lander, and Nye counties in Nevada. Its water purification technology used to recover and extract lithium from brine solutions. The company was formerly known as Golden Aria Corp. and changed its name to Enertopia Corp. in February 2010. Enertopia Corp. was founded in 2004 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.


1130 West Pender StreetSuite 950Vancouver, BC V6E 4A4CanadaFounded in 2004



Phone: 604-602-1675

Fax: 604-685-1602

www.enertopia.com







