Green Canvas — Enertopia Corporation

















































































Green Canvas

















































Green Canvas - Regina, SKIn February 2014 Enertopia announced the signing of a joint-venture agreement to acquire up to 75% of the Regina based scalable, Green Canvas MMJ growing facility.The Green Canvas facility is scalable to 55,000 ft² currently undergoing upgrades to make 14,000 square foot production space compliant with MMPR standards.






